title: Stephon Clark's brother protests at Sacramento council meeting
text:
Stephon Clark's brother protests at Sacramento council meeting 1:04am IST - 01:24 
Stevonte Clark, the brother of Stephon Clark, who was killed by police on March 18th, interrupted a Sacramento City Council meeting on Tuesday. Rough Cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
